ZUMBA_EVENT_FOR_CHARITY – 27/12/2015
- The_Zumba_Charity_Event with title “ WE_ARE_ALL_TOGETHER_IN_NEW_YEAR_EVE” made by Vui_Khoe_Zumba_Fitness and the charity group named Thiện_Nguyện_Tâm_Ái , is to create a budget to buy gifts for poor people in this coming Lunar_New_Year .
- Ticket price : 80.000 VND/person
- The money from selling tickets will be announced and given to Thiện_Nguyện_Tâm_Ái group in the vegetarian buffet program in the evening of the same date 27/12/2015 . More information about the vegetarian buffet program : https : / / www.facebook.com/events/1503516349951712 /
